@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_lwteba(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = wp.exp((wp.exp(tmp + 0.54) - (tmp + 0.50 - v1 + 0.83)))
    tmp = wp.exp((0.39 / (v2 + 0.60 * v1 + 0.69)))
    v2 = 0.65
    data[tid] = v0
